means	O
may	O
therefore	O
be	O
composed	O
of	O
one	O
or	O
more	O
later	O
stages	O
dealing	O
with	O
two-dimensional	O
signals	O
.	O
In	O
the	O
preferred	O
embodiment	O
,	O
the	O
