means	O
,	O
the	O
pattern	O
recognizing	O
system	O
further	O
comprises	O
a	O
neural	O
network	O
responsive	O
to	O
the	O
two-dimensional	O
representation	O
of	O
this	O
input	O
speech	O
signal	O
for	O
identifying	O
phonemes	O
,	O
groups	O
of	O
phonemes	O
,	O
or	O
suprasegmentals	O
in	O
the	O
input	O
signal	O
,	O
and	O
the	O
filtering	O
means	O
is	O
a	O
