in	O
more	O
detail	O
below	O
.	O

To	O
recognize	O
patterns	O
in	O
an	O
input	O
speech	O
or	O
non-speech	O
sound	O
signal	O
,	O
it	O
is	O
important	O
to	O
improve	O
the	O
