input	O
signal	O
may	O
be	O
recognized	O
during	O
subsequent	O
analysis	O
despite	O
a	O
noisy	O
background	O
.	O
This	O
invention	O
is	O
based	O
on	O
the	O
observation	O
that	O
,	O
by	O
using	O
a	O
plurality	O
of	O
