used	O
for	O
analyzing	O
a	O
space-time	O
two-dimensional	O
representation	O
of	O
handwriting	O
.	O

Cochlear	O
Filter	O
Bank	O
As	O
discussed	O
above	O
,	O
humans	O
or	O
animals	O
such	O
as	O
dogs	O
and	O
cats	O
,	O
have	O
little	O
difficulty	O
in	O
recognizing	O
spoken	O
sounds	O
.	O
For	O
this	O
reason	O
,	O
research	O
and	O
development	O
in	O
speech	O
recognition	O
have	O
used	O
models	O
of	O
the	O
biological	O
cochlear	O
for	O
designing	O
machines	O
which	O
can	O
emulate	O
the	O
function	O
of	O
a	O
biological	O
cochlear	O
in	O
recognizing	O
speech	O
in	O
spoken	O
sounds	O
.	O
Before	O
a	O
cochlear	O
model	O
is	O
considered	O
,	O
however	O
,	O
it	O
will	O
be	O
useful	O
to	O
first	O
review	O
the	O
general	O
function	O
and	O
construction	O
of	O
the	O
cochlear	O
.	O
The	O
