a	O
mechanical	O
connection	O
which	O
includes	O
the	O
stapes	O
.	O
The	O
chamber	O
surrounding	O
the	O
basilar	O
membrane	O
is	O
filled	O
with	O
a	O
fluid	O
which	O
is	O
essentially	O
water	O
.	O
When	O
